	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wrote 81, a PCM WAVE to NES DPCM converter. I have used it to convert a minute and a half long sample spread over numerous MMC3 banks. Go to nesdev.com and look for "sample converter by Damian Yerrick".

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


