		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">bucky o'hare wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Only the DPCM converter never wanted play full songs for me. For a longer fill I wanted to sample from a new order song, I had to break it into several short wavs, convert them individually, and then piece them back together. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" /> </div>
<br />A DPCM waveform can't be longer than about 32 Ksamples. If you're running at the highest sample rate, this is just under 1 second.

		

		</td>
